      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、疲れてませんか？　昨日はライブだったし\n新幹線で少しは眠ってくれて良かったのに",
      "startTime": 5.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "け、結構よ……\n昨日は打ち上げの後、ぐっすり眠ったから",
      "startTime": 10.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "……貴方が実家に来るのが気になって\n眠るどころじゃなかったわよ！",
      "startTime": 17.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　何か言いましたか？",
      "startTime": 19.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんでもないわよ！\n独り言を聞かないでちょうだい！",
      "startTime": 24,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6766.666666700001,
          "startTime": 30.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……母に電話を掛けるから\nそこでちょっと待っていてもらえる？",
      "startTime": 30.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "――もしもし、お母さん？\n今日これからそっちに帰るつもりなんだけど……",
      "startTime": 36.8666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "その……紹介したい人を連れて行ってもいいかしら？",
      "startTime": 39.8333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "riomam",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-riomom001.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、大歓迎よ\n楽しいお正月になりそうね。お友達？",
      "startTime": 46.5000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "……友達じゃないわ。私のマネージャーよ",
      "startTime": 50.1000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "riomam",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-riomom002.m4a",
      "text": "まあまあ！　莉央が前、話してくれた方ね！\n若いのに、とっても優秀で将来が楽しみな男性だって",
      "startTime": 57.7333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そこまでは言ってないわよ\nとにかく、彼が挨拶をしたいって言ってるの",
      "startTime": 65.3000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "嫌ならいいの。私がうまく言っておくから――",
      "startTime": 68.7666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "riomam",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-riomom003.m4a",
      "text": "何を言ってるの。もちろんお会いするわ\n日頃、莉央がお世話になっているお礼を言わないと",
      "startTime": 75.2333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "……そ、そう",
      "startTime": 78.6000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "riomam",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-riomom004.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、莉央がお正月に男性を\n連れて来るなんて……！　お母さん、嬉しいわ",
      "startTime": 83.5666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　ちょっとお母さん、そういう意味じゃ――",
      "startTime": 87.9666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "riomam",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-riomom005.m4a",
      "text": "歓迎の準備をして待ってるわね、それじゃ後で！",
      "startTime": 90.5666676839,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-end-03.m4a",
          "delay": 4266.6666667000045,
          "startTime": 94.8333343506
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "待って、お母さん！　彼はそんなんじゃ……\n……電話、切れてる",
      "startTime": 98.8666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "ああもう！　すっかり誤解されてるわ！",
      "startTime": 100.8333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと莉央さん、相談があるんですが……\nん？　様子が変ですよ？　どうしたんですか？",
      "startTime": 107.6000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "だから！　なんでもないわよ！\nそれより相談って何よ！！",
      "startTime": 113.9666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "な、何怒ってるんですか……\n莉央さんのお母さんに買ってきたお土産なんですけど",
      "startTime": 118.6000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "普通の菓子折だけで良かったんでしょうか？\n俺としては、喜んでもらえるようもっと気合いを……",
      "startTime": 125.9000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "入れなくていい！　無難でいいの！　そんなことしたら\nお母さんが余計に誤解しちゃうでしょ！？",
      "startTime": 132.8333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "誤解って……何を？",
      "startTime": 135.5000010173,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9833.333333300005,
          "startTime": 145.3333343506
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "だから、私のお母さんが、貴方を……\n言わせないでよ！　馬鹿！　もう！",
      "startTime": 142.0333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、待って下さい！\n……俺、なんで怒られたんだ？",
      "startTime": 149.7666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "riomam",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-riomom006.m4a",
      "text": "遠い所から、わざわざ恐れ入ります\n莉央が大変お世話になっております",
      "startTime": 158.3333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
